{"tid":882026,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【惠英紅受勳】自覺對人生有交代　下一步想嫁人：有臭狐都冇所謂","createTime":"2018-10-30T01:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T01:47:01.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"63c006f4cfd9f9a67469d9b8c4914f2c83e0adab","tid":882026,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:39:22.000Z","msg":"三屆金像影后惠英紅（紅姐）日前獲行政長官林鄭月娥頒授銅紫荊星章，今晚（29日）英皇老闆楊受成在灣仔英皇駿景酒店為其設宴慶祝，金牌經理人霍汶希（Mani）等亦有前來到賀，大會更送上銅紫荊星章造型蛋糕，場面非常高興！<br />\n<br />\n談到獲頒授勳章的感覺，紅姐坦言感覺與在電影頒獎禮上獲獎不同：「我阿妹同我講『都算係咁』，我個感覺都係『都算係咁』，好似對自己人生有所交代咁。」問下一個目標，她說：「嫁得出！（嫁個有錢人？）嫁個好人！就算對方有大肚腩、臭狐都冇所謂。」她直言一路以來都有親朋好友介紹男生予她認識，但見面後總是誤以為她是女強人：「好似俾人判咗死刑咁！其實我都唔係好事業型女性、唔係咁強勢，有一次有人介紹我同個男性食飯，我好乖坐喺度，但我耳仔同眼都唔好，唔係好畀到反應對方，佢以為我好Cool。係，我本身係做戲，我唔想喺人面前做戲，但我真係唔強，我係波斯貓嚟，只係生得似獅子。」<br />\n<br />\n提到21年的感情空白期，紅姐坦言之前曾經和一位男士拍拖一星期，分手原因是男方友人指自己睇過她的寫真集覺得好索，而男友又煞有介事地向她轉述這段說話，所以她深知對方心底裏無法接受便主動提出分手：「我30歲時去過睇紫微斗數，師傅批我60幾歲先有對象，老咗先有伴，我之後拎住本命書喺公園睇到喊！」現在58歲的她便指希望師傅能夠批得中，讓她可以老來有伴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2029495/org/3e3ca74046ad2386ccaae19da9ef81ea.jpeg/oSWYLd43y_cUXlJSqbSuiZV2puoOr2XxHWQBsR1kAbE?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2029495%2Forg%2F3e3ca74046ad2386ccaae19da9ef81ea.jpeg%2FoSWYLd43y_cUXlJSqbSuiZV2puoOr2XxHWQBsR1kAbE%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=eeceb3a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2029503/org/d5f5ef82fab81511fe6ce9bf1b76ba25.jpeg/Xv9FIagUiwnVCDVKyUmw7YEVJN2A0R_DiAukTKILpEw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2029503%2Forg%2Fd5f5ef82fab81511fe6ce9bf1b76ba25.jpeg%2FXv9FIagUiwnVCDVKyUmw7YEVJN2A0R_DiAukTKILpEw&h=a2c77040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2029496/org/b87f0812cb3cc17f544c36520c4ca1db.jpeg/jFqC2RJ9DSCFNs4Cak2pj0dF9XMai0KYRtk5HWzZOR0?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2029496%2Forg%2Fb87f0812cb3cc17f544c36520c4ca1db.jpeg%2FjFqC2RJ9DSCFNs4Cak2pj0dF9XMai0KYRtk5HWzZOR0%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=68f18699&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd5bab032d9781e17540c210854367640f9cdd16","tid":882026,"uid":32403,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:16:13.000Z","msg":"推薦連登一位巴打<br />\n棋靈王"},{"pid":"f4b8936228a51a3c516ac5d5f5a0fd95668ac407","tid":882026,"uid":81562,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"fd5bab032d9781e17540c210854367640f9cdd16","tid":882026,"uid":32403,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:16:13.000Z","msg":"推薦連登一位巴打<br />\n棋靈王"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:40:05.000Z","msg":"紅姐呢d後生女邊岩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a63671a5d0373d6cb73386f9b9430288ee2b024","tid":882026,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"想埋單"},{"pid":"8611f8c7f0b61dd413aee9b905d6d27c52e9d9aa","tid":882026,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/122812_cdb7f43560e436c50b06eb9be125323f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F122812_cdb7f43560e436c50b06eb9be125323f.gif&h=d012834d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"caf01e35adcd28752d95d53869108dd8cc72a6c4","tid":882026,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T01:47:01.000Z","msg":"LM"}]}